#Abyssinia_Bank 

The First Bank in Ethiopia to acquire PCI DSS v4.0 ‚Äì Level 1

In its effort to elevate security and enhance customer safety, Bank of Abyssinia proudly announces its compliance with PCI DSS ‚Äì Level 1 for the second consecutive year, in v4.0 this time. We are also a valued Visa Global Registry service provider. Acquiring PCI DSS in v4.0 makes Bank of Abyssinia the first in Ethiopia and among the few in East Africa, showcasing its commitment to securing your data. This certification, from the Payment Card Industry Council, ensures the security of sensitive card data and prevents fraud, promoting trustworthy transactions for our customers.
